---
import { href } from '../utils';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer>
  <div class="inner">
    <p>
      <strong>SPPS EdTech</strong> is an independent, parent-run resource. It is not
      affiliated with, or endorsed by, Saint Paul Public Schools.
    </p>
    <p>
      This site is not anti-technology. It exists to help families and educators
      distinguish pedagogically purposeful technology from addictive and
      distracting technology — and to keep district policy accountable to the
      evidence.
    </p>
    <p>
      Every factual claim links to its source. Spot an error or an outdated fact?
      <a href="https://github.com/kgerbner/SPPSEdTech/issues">Let us know</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="fine">© {year} SPPS EdTech · <a href={href('/learn-more/')}>Sources &amp; further reading</a></p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  footer {
    background: var(--navy-dark);
    color: #d8dde4;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .inner {
    max-width: var(--wide);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.25rem;
  }
  footer a { color: #fff; }
  .fine { opacity: 0.7; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
</style>
